<h1>Rider Application Received 🏍</h1>
<p>Hi <strong style="color:#F0F0F0;">{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>
  Thank you for signing up as a NduthiRide rider! Your application has been received
  and is currently under review.
</p>

<hr class="divider" />

<h2>Application Summary</h2>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">License Number</span>
  <span class="info-value">{{licenseNumber}}</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">Bike Registration</span>
  <span class="info-value">{{bikeRegistration}}</span>
</div>
{{#if bikeModel}}
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">Bike Model</span>
  <span class="info-value">{{bikeModel}}</span>
</div>
{{/if}}
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">Status</span>
  <span class="info-value">
    <span class="badge badge-warning">Pending Verification</span>
  </span>
</div>

<hr class="divider" />

<h2>What happens next?</h2>
<p>
  Our team will verify your license and bike documents within <strong style="color:#F0F0F0;">24–48 hours</strong>.
  You will receive an email as soon as your account is approved.
</p>

<div class="alert">
  <strong>Tip:</strong> Make sure your license and bike registration are valid and up to date.
  Applications with expired documents will be rejected.
</div>

<p style="text-align:center;">
  <a href="{{appUrl}}" class="btn">Open Rider App</a>
</p>
